prompt_text: Describe the smartphone application that you use the most.
content_text: My favorite smartphone application is Instagram. I use it on a daily basis, maybe a little too much. And it is a great way to connect with friends that I've lost touch with or my friends that have moved abroad. I can keep in touch with them by seeing what they're up to in their day-to-day lives. It is also a good way to share my thoughts. And opinions about things and it. Also acts as. A relief after work when I'm trying to wind down.
